# ****DAY 1****
Today we will focus on **setting up the project.**
1. Create a project folder on your computer (e.g., Professional-Portfolio).
2. Initialize Git:
```bash
git init
```
3. Create basic files: index.html and style.css.
4. Make your first commit:
```bash
git add .
git commit -m "Initial commit: setup project folder and basic files"
```
